                    'description' => 'Création d\'un nouvel événement',
                    'subject_type' => 'App\\Models\\EventAnnouncement',
                    'subject_id' => 5,
                    'causer_type' => 'App\\Models\\User',
                    'causer_id' => 1,
                'properties' => '{"titre fr":"Salon international des fa\\u00e7ades fen\\u00eatres et portes (clon\\u00e9)","description fr":"LA R\\u00c9F\\u00c9RENCE INTERNATIONALE DES FA\\u00c7ADES, FEN\\u00caTRES & PORTES !","contenu fr":"<p>La <strong>7\\u00e8me \\u00e9dition<\\/strong> du Salon International des Fa\\u00e7ades, Fen\\u00eatres et Portes ouvre ses portes du <strong>20 au 23 Septembre<\\/strong> \\u00e0 Alger. Un rendez-vous unique pour :<\\/p><ul><li><strong>D\\u00e9couvrir<\\/strong> les derni\\u00e8res technologies (isolation, design, s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9).<\\/li><li><strong>\\u00c9changer<\\/strong> avec les industriels locaux et internationaux.<\\/li><li><strong>Apprendre<\\/strong> lors des workshops pratiques d\\u00e9di\\u00e9s aux professionnels.<br>Avec <strong>10 000 visiteurs attendus<\\/strong>, le SIFFP confirme sa place de hub strat\\u00e9gique pour le secteur !<\\/li><li><strong>SIFFP 2025 EN 5 CHIFFRES :<\\/strong><ul><li><strong>7<\\/strong> ans d\\u2019expertise<\\/li><li><strong>150+<\\/strong> exposants<\\/li><li><strong>10 000+<\\/strong> visiteurs professionnels<\\/li><li><strong>6 000 m\\u00b2<\\/strong> d\\u2019innovations<\\/li><li><strong>15+<\\/strong> conf\\u00e9rences th\\u00e9matiques<br>\\ud83d\\udca1 <strong>Ne manquez pas l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement phare de l\\u2019architecture en Alg\\u00e9rie !<\\/strong><\\/li><li>\\ud83d\\udcc5 <strong>20-23 Septembre 2025<\\/strong> \\u2022 \\ud83d\\udccd <strong>Safex, Alger<\\/strong><\\/li><\\/ul><\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><br><\\/p><p><br><br><\\/p>","conditions fr":"<h3>1. <strong>Objet<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>Les pr\\u00e9sentes conditions g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rales d\\u00e9finissent les r\\u00e8gles de participation au <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong>, organis\\u00e9 au <strong>Safex (Pavilion Central) Alger<\\/strong> du <strong>20 au 23 septembre 2025<\\/strong>.<\\/p><h3>2. <strong>Inscription et Acc\\u00e8s<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>La participation \\u00e0 l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement est ouverte aux <strong>professionnels et au grand public<\\/strong>.<\\/li><li>L\\u2019acc\\u00e8s au salon est conditionn\\u00e9 par <strong>une inscription pr\\u00e9alable<\\/strong> via le site officiel ou sur place.<\\/li><li>L\\u2019organisateur se r\\u00e9serve le droit de <strong>refuser l\\u2019entr\\u00e9e<\\/strong> \\u00e0 toute personne ne respectant pas les r\\u00e8gles de l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>3. <strong>R\\u00e8glement Int\\u00e9rieur<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Les visiteurs doivent se conformer aux <strong>normes de s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9<\\/strong> et respecter les instructions du personnel.<\\/li><li>Il est interdit de <strong>filmer ou photographier<\\/strong> sans autorisation pr\\u00e9alable.<\\/li><li>Tout comportement inappropri\\u00e9 peut entra\\u00eener <strong>l\\u2019expulsion imm\\u00e9diate<\\/strong> sans remboursement.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>4. <strong>Responsabilit\\u00e9s<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>L\\u2019organisateur ne pourra \\u00eatre tenu responsable en cas de <strong>vol, perte ou dommage<\\/strong> des biens personnels des visiteurs.<\\/li><li>En cas d\\u2019annulation ou de modification de l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement, les participants seront inform\\u00e9s dans les meilleurs d\\u00e9lais.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>5. <strong>Donn\\u00e9es Personnelles<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Les informations collect\\u00e9es lors de l\\u2019inscription sont utilis\\u00e9es uniquement pour la gestion de l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement et ne seront <strong>pas partag\\u00e9es avec des tiers<\\/strong>.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>6. <strong>Acceptation des Conditions<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>La participation au <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong> implique <strong>l\\u2019acceptation totale<\\/strong> des pr\\u00e9sentes conditions g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rales.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><\\/p>","titre en":"International Exhibition of Window and Door Facades (cloned)","description en":"THE INTERNATIONAL REFERENCE FOR FACADES, WINDOWS AND DOORS!","contenu en":"<p>The 7th edition of the International Exhibition of Facades, Windows and Doors opens its doors from September 20th to 23rd in Algiers. A unique opportunity to:<br><br>Discover the latest technologies (insulation, design, security).<br>Interact with local and international manufacturers.<br>Learn during practical workshops dedicated to professionals.<br>With 10,000 visitors expected, the SIFFP confirms its position as a strategic hub for the sector!<br>SIFFP 2025 IN 5 FIGURES:<br>7 years of expertise<br>150+ exhibitors<br>10,000+ professional visitors<br>6,000 m\\u00b2 of innovations<br>15+ thematic conferences<br>\\ud83d\\udca1 Don\'t miss the flagship architecture event in Algeria!<br>\\ud83d\\udcc5 September 20-23, 2025 \\u2022 \\ud83d\\udccd Safex, Algiers<\\/p>","conditions en":"<h3>1. <strong>Purpose<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>These general terms and conditions define the rules for participation in <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong>, scheduled to take place at <strong>Safex (Central Pavilion) Algiers<\\/strong> from <strong>September 20 to 23, 2025<\\/strong>.<\\/p><h3>2. <strong>Registration &amp; Access<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Participation is open to <strong>professionals and the general public<\\/strong>.<\\/li><li>Entry to the exhibition requires <strong>prior registration<\\/strong> through the official website or on-site.<\\/li><li>The organizer reserves the right to <strong>deny entry<\\/strong> to anyone not complying with event rules.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>3. <strong>Internal Regulations<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Visitors must follow <strong>safety protocols<\\/strong> and respect staff instructions.<\\/li><li><strong>Photography and filming<\\/strong> are prohibited without prior authorization.<\\/li><li>Any inappropriate behavior may result in <strong>immediate expulsion<\\/strong> without refund.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>4. <strong>Liabilities<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>The organizer is not responsible for <strong>theft, loss, or damage<\\/strong> of visitors\\u2019 personal