                'properties' => '{"conditions fr ancien":null,"conditions fr nouveau":"<h3>1. <strong>Objet<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>Les pr\\u00e9sentes conditions g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rales d\\u00e9finissent les r\\u00e8gles de participation au <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong>, organis\\u00e9 au <strong>Safex (Pavilion Central) Alger<\\/strong> du <strong>20 au 23 septembre 2025<\\/strong>.<\\/p><h3>2. <strong>Inscription et Acc\\u00e8s<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>La participation \\u00e0 l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement est ouverte aux <strong>professionnels et au grand public<\\/strong>.<\\/li><li>L\\u2019acc\\u00e8s au salon est conditionn\\u00e9 par <strong>une inscription pr\\u00e9alable<\\/strong> via le site officiel ou sur place.<\\/li><li>L\\u2019organisateur se r\\u00e9serve le droit de <strong>refuser l\\u2019entr\\u00e9e<\\/strong> \\u00e0 toute personne ne respectant pas les r\\u00e8gles de l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>3. <strong>R\\u00e8glement Int\\u00e9rieur<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Les visiteurs doivent se conformer aux <strong>normes de s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9<\\/strong> et respecter les instructions du personnel.<\\/li><li>Il est interdit de <strong>filmer ou photographier<\\/strong> sans autorisation pr\\u00e9alable.<\\/li><li>Tout comportement inappropri\\u00e9 peut entra\\u00eener <strong>l\\u2019expulsion imm\\u00e9diate<\\/strong> sans remboursement.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>4. <strong>Responsabilit\\u00e9s<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>L\\u2019organisateur ne pourra \\u00eatre tenu responsable en cas de <strong>vol, perte ou dommage<\\/strong> des biens personnels des visiteurs.<\\/li><li>En cas d\\u2019annulation ou de modification de l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement, les participants seront inform\\u00e9s dans les meilleurs d\\u00e9lais.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>5. <strong>Donn\\u00e9es Personnelles<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Les informations collect\\u00e9es lors de l\\u2019inscription sont utilis\\u00e9es uniquement pour la gestion de l\\u2019\\u00e9v\\u00e9nement et ne seront <strong>pas partag\\u00e9es avec des tiers<\\/strong>.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>6. <strong>Acceptation des Conditions<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>La participation au <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong> implique <strong>l\\u2019acceptation totale<\\/strong> des pr\\u00e9sentes conditions g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rales.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>","conditions en ancien":null,"conditions en nouveau":"<h3>1. <strong>Purpose<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>These general terms and conditions define the rules for participation in <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong>, scheduled to take place at <strong>Safex (Central Pavilion) Algiers<\\/strong> from <strong>September 20 to 23, 2025<\\/strong>.<\\/p><h3>2. <strong>Registration &amp; Access<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Participation is open to <strong>professionals and the general public<\\/strong>.<\\/li><li>Entry to the exhibition requires <strong>prior registration<\\/strong> through the official website or on-site.<\\/li><li>The organizer reserves the right to <strong>deny entry<\\/strong> to anyone not complying with event rules.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>3. <strong>Internal Regulations<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Visitors must follow <strong>safety protocols<\\/strong> and respect staff instructions.<\\/li><li><strong>Photography and filming<\\/strong> are prohibited without prior authorization.<\\/li><li>Any inappropriate behavior may result in <strong>immediate expulsion<\\/strong> without refund.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>4. <strong>Liabilities<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>The organizer is not responsible for <strong>theft, loss, or damage<\\/strong> of visitors\\u2019 personal belongings.<\\/li><li>In case of event cancellation or modification, participants will be informed as soon as possible.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>5. <strong>Personal Data<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Information collected during registration is used <strong>only for event management<\\/strong> and will <strong>not be shared with third parties<\\/strong>.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>6. <strong>Acceptance of Terms<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul><li>Participation in <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong> implies <strong>full acceptance<\\/strong> of these terms and conditions.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>","conditions ar ancien":null,"conditions ar nouveau":"<h3 dir=\\"rtl\\">1. <strong>\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0648\\u0636\\u0648\\u0639<\\/strong><\\/h3><p dir=\\"rtl\\">\\u062a\\u062d\\u062f\\u062f \\u0647\\u0630\\u0647 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u0631\\u0648\\u0637 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u062d\\u0643\\u0627\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0642\\u0648\\u0627\\u0639\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u0627\\u0645\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0645\\u0634\\u0627\\u0631\\u0643\\u0629 \\u0641\\u064a <strong>SIFFP 2025<\\/strong>\\u060c \\u0627\\u0644\\u0630\\u064a \\u0633\\u064a\\u0642\\u0627\\u0645 \\u0641\\u064a <strong>\\u0633\\u0627\\u0641\\u0643\\u0633 (\\u0627\\u0644\\u062c\\u0646\\u0627\\u062d \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0631\\u0643\\u0632\\u064a) \\u0627\\u0644\\u062c\\u0632\\u0627\\u0626\\u0631<\\/strong> \\u0645\\u0646 <strong>20 \\u0625\\u0644\\u0649 23 \\u0633\\u0628\\u062a\\u0645\\u0628\\u0631 2025<\\/strong>.<\\/p><h3 dir=\\"rtl\\">2. <strong>\\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0633\\u062c\\u064a\\u0644 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u062f\\u062e\\u0648\\u0644<\\/strong><\\/h3><ul dir=\\"rtl\\"><li>\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0634\\u0627\\u0631\\u0643\\u0629 \\u0645\\u0641\\u062a\\u0648\\u062d\\u0629 \\u0623\\u0645\\u0627\\u0645 <strong>\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0647\\u0646\\u064a\\u064a\\u0646 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u062c\\u0645\\u0647\\u0648\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u0627\\u0645<\\/strong>.<\\/li><li>\\u064a\\u062a\\u0637\\u0644\\u0628 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062f\\u062e\\u0648\\u0644 \\u0625\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0631\\u0636 <strong>\\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0633\\u062c\\u064a\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u0628\\u0642<\\/strong> \\u0639\\u0628\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0648\\u0642\\u0639 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0631\\u0633\\u0645\\u064a \\u0623\\u0648 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0627\\u0644\\u06